{"tid":1043464,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"上下失守！深田恭子深V倒出兇猛車頭燈 高衩美腿被看光","createTime":"2019-03-02T09:44:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-02T14:34:33.000Z","uid":32511,"like":6,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"8712232bdc251ce1a8e7ccc2752de14dc9f4f946","tid":1043464,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T09:44:55.000Z","msg":"有「日本奧斯卡」之稱的「日本電影金像獎」，昨舉辦頒獎典禮，現場星光熠熠，其中深田恭子一襲深V又開高衩雪白禮服，「上下失守」艷壓全場，火辣程度讓網友全都驚呆。<br />\n<br />\n深田恭子以《飛上天空的輪胎》入圍最佳女配角，不過她也以火辣身材著稱，曾出過性感寫真集，這次禮服果然沒讓大家失望，她身穿一襲深V爆乳、開高衩直逼腿根雪白女神禮服，還坐在高腳椅和主持人對話，不僅美腿被看光，腿間宇宙領域若隱若現引起遐想。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/02/174450_c439cce93796f71ac2958c316c8e7acc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F02%2F174450_c439cce93796f71ac2958c316c8e7acc.jpg&h=835496ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/02/174450_16f2fa0a7a32611ac3c7a698901f7b14.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F02%2F174450_16f2fa0a7a32611ac3c7a698901f7b14.jpg&h=543b2a90&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/02/174450_84fe6b2dc6943d9ce7e8ef0fbf2a279d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F02%2F174450_84fe6b2dc6943d9ce7e8ef0fbf2a279d.jpg&h=1cab0626&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/02/174450_0ff3b62e5678b348a9148775680db7cc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F02%2F174450_0ff3b62e5678b348a9148775680db7cc.jpg&h=b614d9cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/02/174451_61d723c8425e85e5f00b21a6b60e885a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F02%2F174451_61d723c84